videos.description: Nelson Boachie-Yiadom bounces a pass in between two defenders for Hyunjung Lee, and Lee extends backwards to get the layup in putting Davidson within 2.
videos.headline: Boachie-Yiadom sneaks a pass inside, Lee drives it home
